{"tid":1316293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【文宣集中火力】7月14，警方犯法行為？","createTime":"2019-07-14T15:47:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T00:44:03.000Z","uid":38177,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"02a6b2ecf5dea07935b2caa251862fcb9a73dac4","tid":1316293,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:47:49.000Z","msg":"剛剛係街度聽到人地討論緊警方行動，想問下大家係咪真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.新城市廣場已宣報從無報警或向警方求助<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">根據第《警察通例- 44 章 搜查人身、處所及車輛, 44-04 搜查處所》，1. 警務人員如未獲得合法授權或擁有人╱佔用人的同意，不得進入任何處所搜查。 </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">即是代表，所有警察在廣場內所有執勤，拘捕行動</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">均屬違法</span><br />\n<br />\n2.有冒警犯人<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">（無出示委任證）</span>手持警察裝備<span style=\"font-size: small;\">懷疑盗用警務人員裝備</span>於新城市廣場襲擊市民，一名市民趕他落電梯，一眾市民把他制服。<br />\n<br />\n3.有大量情況，警員在拘捕過程中，沒有回應議員提問，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">沒有解釋市民該犯罪行便以暴力拘捕並帶走，嚴重違法警察通例</span>，犯法情況下暴力禁錮市民，並且在拘捕過程中，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">沒有進行警誡程序，足以證明拘捕行動不合法</span>，現在有議員向犯法行為報案，但其他警察沒有理會，這行為證明，<span style=\"color: red;\">所有在場既警察嚴重違紀違法</span><br />\n<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: red;\">造謠中傷誹謗市民</span>驅散過程中，有警員嗌咪，誣蔑市民向警員投擲石塊，但在場議員及記者，沒有看到什麼市民投擲石塊，直指警察造謠生事，<span style=\"color: red;\">嚴重失德</span><br />\n<br />\n5.有白衣警員在陽岳橋議員查問下，透露出警方的圍捕行動，而非驅散行動，警方行動令事件升溫，造成混亂，令大量市民恐慌，警方所作所為均造成公眾恐慌，嚴重破壞和平示威活動，打壓人權。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">警察盡忠職守，有乜可能會做依啲野，支持成立獨立委員會，還香港警察一個清白<br />\n</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de281f2e22f68ba86743ef6b01e69726c66158e2","tid":1316293,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:48:41.000Z","msg":"還警察一個清白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89eddaacbcc3de7ac24e9fb5b0a84adef8d90b3d","tid":1316293,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:50:08.000Z","msg":"唔相信盡忠職守既警察會做依啲咁既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不服來辯"},{"pid":"b8311f65c777cf51a600316d6f84f9a3698a5d6c","tid":1316293,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:50:51.000Z","msg":"警察係代表公義，點會犯法，我要以正視聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c9a269817498279ffd1af73f5a273cc0bef2e72","tid":1316293,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:51:39.000Z","msg":"推到全世界都知警察係遵守法紀"},{"pid":"b0199204565093c7029c8f737b20a39f03798435","tid":1316293,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:52:08.000Z","msg":"人手置頂"},{"pid":"7706a3cf64a575e428d2a3e6cc825dfa8766270d","tid":1316293,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:52:46.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb1ed592a6a2d61ba24aacce4d12127c1738e40","tid":1316293,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:53:26.000Z","msg":"選擇性失明？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f77884ee4e5421590a655fa1036dedb8ad0884","tid":1316293,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:53:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a1caa25edc8d3fe101025fc2d7df7614a91735","tid":1316293,"uid":159997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:55:52.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"8564914ed721080d4e2657f3322d53b71c2b0027","tid":1316293,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:56:18.000Z","msg":"隔離post都話，係冒警既恐怖分子，唔係警察，好彩ja，警察點會犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重申！冇警察比人打！市民係制服一名恐怖分子<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1316050\" data-auto-link targ